name: ROYALTON Luxury Car and Limousine Service
overview: ROYALTON Luxury Car and Limousine offers discounted yet excellent and luxurious limousine service to and from the Newark (EWR), John F. Kennedy (JFK), LaGuardia (LGA) Airport and Cruise Ships. ROYALTON car and limousine service also provides Discounted Point to Point Service. ROYALTON has been serving New York, New Jersey, Connecticut and Pennsylvania Airports for many years, with countless satisfied individual and corporate clients. Our team of friendly and courteous drivers possesses the knowledge, experience, and skills to ensure that the passengers travel comfortably, safely, and luxuriously. This combined know-how, the state of the art limo service, quality of our cars enables us to provide the most professional service to each and every client. We provide 24 hours a day 7 days a week service. All cars and drivers are fully licensed and insured. Although we can usually accommodate our customers on short notice; however, we do recommend that you make your reservations at least 24 hours in advance. CALL US NOW 1.866.840.4141
